    {
      "id": "PopularPost286122",
      "post_content": "It should be fun to use this one with [Children of Korlis](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Children of Korlis) and [Tainted Sigil](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tainted Sigil).  \nThen not only will your opponent take the damage as well, but you'll entirely recover from the attack as well, or even gain twice the amount of life lost this way.  \nJust make sure your opponent doesn't kill you off with the attack. Maybe consider an [Angel's Grace](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Angel's Grace) to ensure that.  \n  \nAnd to ensure that the creatures attack, use [siren](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=siren) effects. You can also choose good old [Maddening Imp](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Maddening Imp) (which again is a remake of [an Imp that existed since Alpha](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=73)).  \n  \nToo bad [Gideon Jura](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gideon Jura) won't work the way this card is worded, otherwise it'd be a pretty awesome combo.",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost286122\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">It should be fun to use this one with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Children of Korlis\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Children of Korlis\">Children of Korlis</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Tainted Sigil\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tainted Sigil\">Tainted Sigil</a>.<br/>Then not only will your opponent take the damage as well, but you'll entirely recover from the attack as well, or even gain twice the amount of life lost this way.<br/>Just make sure your opponent doesn't kill you off with the attack. Maybe consider an <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Angel's Grace\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Angel's Grace\">Angel's Grace</a> to ensure that.<br/><br/>And to ensure that the creatures attack, use <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"siren\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=siren\">siren</a> effects. You can also choose good old <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Maddening Imp\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Maddening Imp\">Maddening Imp</a> (which again is a remake of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"73\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=73\">an Imp that existed since Alpha</a>).<br/><br/>Too bad <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Gideon Jura\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gideon Jura\">Gideon Jura</a> won't work the way this card is worded, otherwise it'd be a pretty awesome combo.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '286122'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy416\">Mode</span>\r\n                                (12/15/2012 2:43:10 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
